Usage: modifyPipelineNetGroup [-help] <netGroupName> [-endReserve <val>]
                              [-endTerm <list>] [-inst <list>] [-net <list>]
                              [-startReserve <val>] [-startTerm <list>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<netGroupName>          # name of net group (string, required)
-endReserve <val>       # reserved distance at end (float, optional)
-endTerm <list>         # list of ending terms (string, optional)
-inst <list>            # list of instance names or patterns (string, optional)
-net <list>             # list of net names or patterns (string, optional)
-startReserve <val>     # reserved distance at start (float, optional)
-startTerm <list>       # list of starting terms (string, optional)